October 24, 2015 Live updates: Miami Hurricanes vs. Clemson Tigers 
UM hosts Clemson at Sun Life Stadium in Miami Gardens at noon on Saturday, Oct. 24 
Miami Herald sportswriters Susan Miller Degnan and Manny Navarro provide live updates Miami Herald sportswriter Susan Miller Degnan previews UM's matchup against Clemson at Sun Life Stadium on Saturday, Oct. 24, 2015.
